Cell[TextData[{
 "The equivalence of the two quantum circuits follows from the ",
 ButtonBox["relation between the SWAP gate and the CNOT gate",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/tutorial/TwoQubitGates#1218939314"],
 ". In fact, the CNOT gate is the inverse of itself, and the above equivalent \
quantum circuit on the right-hand side can be further simplified as follows,"
}], "TechNoteText",
 CellID->564195060,ExpressionUUID->"49339d3a-42ea-4d48-9a03-28ed7cd216da"],

