 CellID->2024715025,ExpressionUUID->"ce88787d-7ce3-4d7d-9733-a32082ce2821"],

Cell["\<\
This equivalent quantum circuit was used by Smolin and DiVincenzo (1996) for \
an efficient implementation of the Fredkin gate in terms of the elementary \
gates . This is illustrated in the following demonstration .\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1348781007,ExpressionUUID->"4c2b6eaa-e710-44d8-b056-ce0f340609a0"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Demonstration", "Subsection",
 CellID->1197675653,ExpressionUUID->"7fef7257-f807-430c-a189-8b41206e51a6"],

Cell["\<\
This shows the quantum circuit model of the quantum Fredkin gate.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1198916797,ExpressionUUID->"76a90ab6-07c7-48c5-955d-802b252f0f8b"],

